User tools for manipulating user credentials.

/-------/
arcproxy:

/-------/
arcslcs:

examples
 ./arcslcs -S https://127.0.0.1:60000/slcs -I https://idp.testshib.org/idp/shibboleth -U myself -P myself -D /home/wzqiang/arc-0.9/src/clients/credentials -c client.xml
./arcslcs -S https://127.0.0.1:60000/slcs -I https://squark.uio.no/idp/shibboleth -U staff -P 123456 -D /home/wzqiang/arc-0.9/src/clients/credentials -c client.xml

All the options can also be configured in the client.xml file.
For testing against the test-purpose Identity Provider. The following username can be used:
staff, researcher, librarian, binduser 
with the same password "123456"

